Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.76,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:34.08,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:41.94,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:49.30,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:53.85,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:58.50,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:06.08,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:12.60,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:20.46,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:27.40,song-op,Song:,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:39.57,eptitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(383,53)}Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:39.57,eptitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(235,51)}Mini Typhoon\N Approaching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:51.94,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, my bangs are getting too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.35,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I should have it trimmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:56.65,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ugly face.  What an ugly face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  What do you mean ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.95,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, it's not the same voice.  Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:15.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.63,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Ugly face, did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:34.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You can't laugh.  You're my twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:39.69,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet somebody was kidding.  I bet you were staring at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:42.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.63,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But his voice was just behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody else was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.39,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from the guy you shouted at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.55,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking it might have been telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.  That's too farfetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, you want me to take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.95,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:12.97,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to buy garlic.  Tomomi, can you..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:13.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.78,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.09,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.08,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:00.05,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Darn Tomomi.  She wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.18,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:22.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.11,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Garlic?  She stinks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.39,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:49.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mikage, how much garlic did you throw in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,The whole pack, so about thirteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.99,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We've got school to go to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:00.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's more delicious with more garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:03.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom has to go to work tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.48,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,People mess up once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.70,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,But it still doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.99,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,The contents spewing out of a canister I hadn't even touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.97,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,The cap was on too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could that be telekinesis?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:34.18,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,There's been strange things happening these last few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.51,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Like towels falling of the shelf all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.26,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Scissors and curlers are misplaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:43.65,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody else says it's probably just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.20,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.45,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, you're getting too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.24,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Really.  You should take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:57.56,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but I have reservations tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:58.49,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Regular customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:02.03,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's a lawyer, so she's very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:07.52,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,She wants me to do her hair, so I can't take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.61,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, can you bring me the towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.43,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.09,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,And then can you mop the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.09,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:26.00,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,You must always be smiling in the salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.83,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've been forced to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.51,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.49,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.41,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hello Mrs. Kobayakawa.  I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:41.03,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a rush.  Can you do the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.53,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.27,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, go read some books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.98,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Garlic breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you use telepathy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.53,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you can hear my voice, answer me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.35,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You talked to me, didn't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.69,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Garlic breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.22,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.15,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, don't bother Yuhei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:44.32,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.  He's a very nervous child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.94,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't like talking to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Was that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.97,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.31,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:24.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.  Not just telepathy, he can use telekinesis too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.51,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:33.57,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.66,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:39.06,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That brat must've called me ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:42.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down Mikage.  I'll try him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.06,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuhei-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.39,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:54.31,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me.  You saw me in the beauty salon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.24,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, so you're twins.  Bummer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:06.19,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You talk so differently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:09.64,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shut up.  Mind your own business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're such an ugly kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.13,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.70,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See you, old hag.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.44,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.61,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, when the towels fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:37.56,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,or the shower broke, Yuhei-chan was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.72,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,But he can't be responsible for any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.26,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.  He was away from those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:50.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he can.  With telekinesis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.71,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet it's him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:16.24,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,You slammed into the wall tripping over a cord?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.65,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:23.15,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a kid, so he doesn't know how to control his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.08,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two teach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:30.91,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,About that, he's an obnoxious brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.14,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:55.48,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you interested in ESP?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.87,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Kageura-sensei..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:06.54,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're buying "Challenge to Husbands, 365 Recipes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.14,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to evade my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.57,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:14.00,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?  Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.87,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's him.
Comment: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:49.28,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eye Catch
Comment: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:44.84,Default,title,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls
Comment: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.28,Default,title,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:22.93,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.  Why did you do that?  Even if you're just a kid, you can't get away with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:29.14,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have lousy taste.  Can't you find any better ones?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That was my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.83,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have anything to do with Kageura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:39.76,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, just a teacher?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:45.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you talk with your mouth?  Not with telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.24,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:52.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.57,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, did you see Yuhei-chan come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.27,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.81,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So this house is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.85,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why he's doing tricks on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's a stupid brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:28.79,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, but maybe he was trying to say something to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.04,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:50.04,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, welcome home.  I'll be home late again.  I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:56.69,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,The dinner is in the fridge.  Use the microwave to warm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:02.77,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,At 9, get changed to your pajamas, brush your teeth, and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.00,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use any fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.42,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somebody...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.52,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}... help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:19.78,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.44,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,He said help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.08,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun!  Yuhei-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.84,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun!  Yuhei-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,He's not answering.  He should be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.73,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.03,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?  Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.72,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did you get in, hag?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,The front door was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You did all this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.27,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your mom?  Is she away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:41.85,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave me alone!  Don't come into my home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.45,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun, listen to me.  We were..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.21,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just get out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:55.13,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tomomi.  Why should we waste our time on this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.09,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.29,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.  Mikage, wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.65,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.81,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:16.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't he get lonely being by himself in a big house like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:20.45,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean he can fool around with the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.33,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.07,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him alone, and he'll get bored soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:33.05,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:34.85,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.95,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That was that you, wasn't it Yuhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.26,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.73,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.15,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.38,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:54.56,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's been doing the same trick everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care about other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:59.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I bet your mom's worried too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:03.23,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom doesn't care about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:08.11,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's working every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.18,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She doesn't care about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.23,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:19.03,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.31,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.81,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.43,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun, listen to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.05,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.31,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get killed if we stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:53.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Then lets teleport out with Yuhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.94,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, why did we end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:23.10,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Yuhei-kun's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,At least there's nothing breakable up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.73,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.  We've got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:36.83,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.95,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.38,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let go of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.39,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.13,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:52.32,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.08,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,That has this weird power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.13,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,You ladies are the same, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's calling us ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.76,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,He was calling us ugly hags until a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.85,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's getting married again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.94,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get lonely, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:17.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been agonizing over it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.95,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter now though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we going to stay up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.66,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.59,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,This is teleportation, right?  Teach me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're too young for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.66,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bit too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.00,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:49.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei-kun, is your mom coming home late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.21,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:58.71,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,We better clean up this room before she comes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:01.75,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,You're not telling mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:04.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,There are things other people shouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:07.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But promise us you won't play tricks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.16,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.85,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So, how are we going to explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:19.62,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Like we played tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.46,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good one.  You're 'it', Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.36,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.52,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's out for a date tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.54,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,She's in for a surprise when she comes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:48.24,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,What does it take to break this many things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.48,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.78,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.98,Default,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhei, don't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:57.79,Default,Yuhei,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:09.66,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,So, he was feeling lonely because his mom's getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's one thing, but he must've thought he's the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:18.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  All ESPers are lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.61,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,You don't sound that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:24.33,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Yuhei-kun will be cheerful like Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.41,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.87,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he won't play tricks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.36,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,It could get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.75,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:50.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:53.49,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,All right, who signed me up for track and field?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:56.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that, you're signed up for literature club and travel club too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,\N"Irregular Cherry Front"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way!  There's two Mikage's!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:12.15,credits,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Original air date April 9, 1993.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.73,0:22:07.82,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:11.31,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:18.03,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Matsunaga Tomomi ...Fujieda Nariko\NMatsunaga Mikage........Nagai Noriko
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.43,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:17.96,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:24.57,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Noda Yuhya...........Yamaguchi Kappei\NKurashige Hideaki...Shiozawa Kaneto
