Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:37.95,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:38.00,credits,note,0000,0000,0046,,{\a6}Miracle Girls Original Soundtrack Sony Records SRCL 2574
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:45.52,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Shinichiroh Kageura...Ken Yamaguchi\NDaijohji Rumiko.................Sakuma Rei
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:49.84,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:51.85,credits,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Yamagishi Kouhei.......Nobuh Tobita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:58.33,creditfansub,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a5}Editing, timing, subbing and additional translation by Miwa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:57.95,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say ``I'm sorry,''
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:03.07,creditfansub,Credit,0000,0000,0046,,{\a7}Subtitled by Studio Hooseki.\Nwww.miwasoft.com/hooseki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:05.53,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:11.14,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:14.51,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:20.30,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:22.81,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:26.38,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.51,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:33.68,song-ed,song:,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
